{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Who you are and what this place is\u2014none of that matters. Your primal survival instinct is your only means of salvation. Here, anything can kill you. You\u2019re allowed only one mistake, but it will be your last.<br><i>A fair deal, isn\u2019t it? Want to play?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135260/extras/BLUEMAN_GIF_04_Compressed.gif?t=1738222236\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>You are not alone. He is watching you.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You do not know his name or understand his motives. His pleasure is your despair. He plays with you, turning your life into an endless nightmare.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135260/extras/BLUEMAN_GIF_01_Compressed.gif?t=1738222236\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Do you truly believe you can escape?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will become a prisoner of a grim, distorted world where every action only makes things worse, and each decision leads to new problems. Can you forge a path forward when every step takes you no closer to uncovering the true nature of this place, and with each failure, finding a way out becomes ever more difficult?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135260/extras/BLUEMAN_GIF_02_Compressed.gif?t=1738222236\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features of Our Game</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are no familiar health or sanity indicators here to help you gauge your condition. There\u2019s no inventory to protect yourself or even give a sense of safety. There is only you\u2014and your drive to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135260/extras/BLUEMAN_GIF_03_Compressed.gif?t=1738222236\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Important</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As developers, we have put in a lot of effort to please you. Thank you for your support.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135260/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738222236","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135260/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738222236","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135260/5458d02d1e48cc9673bd90ca419dd1c73cf9d0a1/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738222236","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135260/5458d02d1e48cc9673bd90ca419dd1c73cf9d0a1/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738222236","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Who you are and what this place is\u2014none of that matters. Your primal survival instinct is your only means of salvation. Here, anything can kill you. You\u2019re allowed only one mistake, but it will be your last.<br><i>A fair deal, isn\u2019t it? Want to play?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135260/extras/BLUEMAN_GIF_04_Compressed.gif?t=1738222236\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>You are not alone. He is watching you.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You do not know his name or understand his motives. His pleasure is your despair. He plays with you, turning your life into an endless nightmare.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135260/extras/BLUEMAN_GIF_